’Щ@08b7ebfa1ceb0f2bbacaab7c4f2d9b5cd4b3fdaba3cfb5fa75273dcf6c680f73Ъ(Title: title: polars value-counts
Path: Flags
Content:
``--column, -c {string}``
: Provide a custom name for the count column.
``--sort, -s``
: Whether or not values should be sorted.
``--parallel, -p``
: Use multiple threads when processing.
``--normalize, -n {string}``
: Normalize the counts.
